title: I drew some Jinx :D
body: I drew Jinx{{champion:222}}  for the garen dreadknight skin, as the code from twitter doesn't work for me. If cannot be done, some rp is good too, though it wouldn't help much.

replies.body: Lucky for you we don't need an art trade for Dreadknight Garen! You're welcome to hang onto this sketch for the next time you need a small RP bump. Check your collection now, you should be able to find Garen and the skin now ^_^
